Development Team ----------------------------------------------------------- Anuradha Dilshan (D/BIT/22/0031) JMDR Jayanath (D/BIT/22/0032) PPK Wickramage (D/BIT/22/0012) DTN Wijesuriya (D/BIT/22/0002) ----------------------------------------------------------- • This is a specialized software application that is designed to automate various administrative tasks, such as membership management, event scheduling, membership fees and other payments, and more.
• Overall, the system environment in club management can be complex, depending on the specific needs of the club and its members. A well designed and integrated system environment can help clubs to streamline their operations, improve member engagement, and ultimately, achieve their goals more efficiently.
